WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.900
Your little boyfriend killed

2
00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:03.380
someone, that’s a fact.

3
00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.680
He killed Li Qi’s man,

4
00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:06.680
so it’s only natural Li Qi grabbed him,

5
00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.160
it has nothing to do with me.

6
00:00:08.820 --> 00:00:10.400
Even if Li Qi didn’t grab him,

7
00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:11.900
the police would have.

8
00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:13.260
He can’t escape either way.

9
00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:16.440
I can make Li Qi let him go.

10
00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:20.540
But the condition is you stay by my side.

11
00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:22.880
Be my woman.

12
00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:29.350
I’ll give you three minutes to decide.

13
00:00:29.350 --> 00:00:30.970
How do I choose?

14
00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:32.990
Do I really have to be his woman?

15
00:00:33.110 --> 00:00:34.550
I don’t even like him.

16
00:00:34.710 --> 00:00:36.710
This Hou Jiuling is too terrifying.

17
00:00:36.730 --> 00:00:37.830
Like a ticking time bomb

18
00:00:37.830 --> 00:00:38.710
that could explode at any moment.

19
00:00:39.150 --> 00:00:40.530
If I don’t agree,

20
00:00:41.070 --> 00:00:42.010
how will DS International’s people

21
00:00:42.010 --> 00:00:42.710
treat Wu Tai?

22
00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:44.510
Will they kill him?

23
00:00:49.070 --> 00:00:51.170
Ji Linling, if you walk away now,

24
00:00:51.690 --> 00:00:53.810
get ready to clean up your friend’s body.

25
00:00:54.010 --> 00:00:56.430
Can you really save him?

26
00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:04.620
You have ten seconds left to decide.

27
00:01:05.580 --> 00:01:07.440
If you choose to stay by my side,

28
00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:08.680
come here.